column5: The weather was a bit extreme and foggy but we still managed a couple of good ones. Hopefully the weather holds for another wknd of great open water fishing in January. Still running cranks back 25-75 back.
Good to hear you're still able to get out fishing. Mother nature isn't all bad. I assume we're talking walleye Bob ?  O.K. knucklehead me just noticed the pic. Very nice eyes
